So Nid JG is still rewarding to those who can actually play Nid...

As in like, she's not a face roll jungler aye?
Takes a decent amount of skill to clear camps in the early game because her early clear speed is pretty bad and her sustain evened out by the damage she takes (#sosquish).
Yeah, although she doesn't have any CC she can make effective ganks just through the raw damage.
yes, she can be. I put her on Pantheon Tier. Snowballs hard with early kills.
